messages.message: Ah is the aclmanager app has been deprecated. it’s no longer an app, it got moved into the repo sharing settings. Why are you trying to access this?

Lol I was trying to find out the demo videos of apps like refiner etc 
I found this link shared by someone sometimes back. Do you know where the link to the demos are? @Heymian

I think our demo videos are a bit scattered afaik. Ted has historically been best about putting together these videos, so I would check with him to see if there’s an existing place for them.  We have a few tutorial vides thrown in here: https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1mwaN9g3A67R7ViIhLUA7OibBNHwAmSyw But it’s definitely not comprehensive.
